City/state latitude and longitude reference data

cityStateToLatLong.Rd

Latitude/longitude lookup table assembled from a public GitHub gist for aligning caller workbooks with geospatial tooling.

Usage

cityStateToLatLong

Format

A tibble with four variables:

city

City name.

state

Two-letter postal state abbreviation.

lat

Latitude in decimal degrees.

long

Longitude in decimal degrees.

Source

https://gist.githubusercontent.com/steinbring/e5417af6d1bb95742555866c84e3f91d/raw/186b532887c9738687860aeae5de7a7b2a0ed233/cityStateToLatLong.csv

Value

A tibble mapping U.S. cities and states to their latitude and longitude coordinates.
